Package com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models

Class ListBlobBlocksOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.BlobServiceOptions
      • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.ListBlobBlocksOptions

  • public class ListBlobBlocksOptions
extends BlobServiceOptions
    Represents the options that may be set on a listBlobBlocks request. These options include an optional server timeout for the operation, the lease ID if the blob has an active lease, the snapshot timestamp to get the committed blocks of a snapshot, whether to return the committed block list, and whether to return the uncommitted block list.

        public ListBlobBlocksOptions setLeaseId​(java.lang.String leaseId)

        Note that this value only affects calls made on methods where this ListBlobBlocksOptions instance is passed as a parameter.

      • setSnapshot

        public ListBlobBlocksOptions setSnapshot​(java.lang.String snapshot)
        Sets the snapshot timestamp value used to identify the particular snapshot of the blob to list blocks for. The snapshot timestamp value is an opaque value returned by the server to identify a snapshot. When this option is set, only the list of committed blocks of the snapshot is returned.

        Note that this value only affects calls made on methods where this ListBlobBlocksOptions instance is passed as a parameter.

        Parameters:
        snapshot - A String containing the snapshot timestamp value of the blob snapshot to list.
        Returns:
        A reference to this ListBlobBlocksOptions instance.
